{"tid":469702,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"上條當麻用右手接唔接到崎玉一拳","createTime":"2017-11-15T14:44:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-16T01:53:59.000Z","uid":72480,"like":2,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"91b4c0873b4a40932952f86a2215819810829612","tid":469702,"uid":72480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T14:44:05.000Z","msg":"我認為接唔到 ,你地點睇"},{"pid":"7511288b6ea1c38176083b02a13ba6e9c212ebe5","tid":469702,"uid":60115,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T14:44:42.000Z","msg":"接到"},{"pid":"02e4345ac5e520c2e29f637277c37ff0a173e010","tid":469702,"uid":34293,"like":43,"dislike":6,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T14:45:29.000Z","msg":"你老母當初比隻狗破左處 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後生撚埋你出黎 <br />\n記唔記得呀 <br />\n你老豆係我執返黎架 <br />\n無我大慈大悲 <br />\n你伯爺仲係街度食緊人地d屎ja世侄 <br />\n諗起你岩岩出世個撚樣唔人唔狗咁 <br />\n我而家都吱一聲咁笑出黎 <br />\n契爺我睇住你大 <br />\n你而家走黎我屋企門口 <br />\n又all屎又all尿盛臭架嘛世侄 <br />\n真係狗娘養的(笑)"},{"pid":"318708014927b1995e29424fd43f0cdf1661aba5","tid":469702,"uid":72480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T14:46:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你老母當初比隻狗破左處 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後生撚埋你出黎 <br />\n記唔記得呀 <br />\n你老豆係我執返黎架 <br />\n無我大慈大悲 <br />\n你伯爺仲係街度食緊人地d屎ja世侄 <br />\n諗起你岩岩出世個撚樣唔人唔狗咁 <br />\n我而家都吱一聲咁笑出黎 <br />\n契爺我睇住你大 <br />\n你而家走黎我屋企門口 <br />\n又all屎又all尿盛臭架嘛世侄 <br />\n真係狗娘養的(笑)</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14218a506445a069140bb4cdc7b96feb79e0702f","tid":469702,"uid":56308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T14:46:33.000Z","msg":"接到"},{"pid":"befa1bbf4ce54b1bc4a72e1f20e04aefde43a54a","tid":469702,"uid":129509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T14:46:35.000Z","msg":"接到"},{"pid":"2ff2bff25067cf671daa141397aa0c12d8b47b4d","tid":469702,"uid":33651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T14:46:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>接到</blockquote>"},{"pid":"34476be2eef3fc9b339db59232e1ee339380b014","tid":469702,"uid":45773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T15:05:24.000Z","msg":"咁一方通行接唔接到？"},{"pid":"5b94b8d153b2b198c6539d7159f52e8ed25b8aa7","tid":469702,"uid":78533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T15:14:06.000Z","msg":"之後死"},{"pid":"fd04088c089d865acb1365857b1ca89a7de29f5c","tid":469702,"uid":37890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T15:15:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁一方通行接唔接到？</blockquote><br />\n不如諗下,比一方通行反完<br />\n自己硬食自己一拳頂唔頂得住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8bbf71d71b351f3edb51852c9119b0c2a133d52","tid":469702,"uid":2471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T15:15:58.000Z","msg":"我覺得有幾個睇法"},{"pid":"7b0a71aa1ed8472a458c4385ffd959612a95e490","tid":469702,"uid":2471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T15:16:23.000Z","msg":"想同大家分享"},{"pid":"cd8f5a772e376f731ebc07a2a433554c537675de","tid":469702,"uid":31542,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T15:16:39.000Z","msg":"當麻右手連物理攻擊都頂到嘅咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af87609574a869a90d199405ce8c39a695809775","tid":469702,"uid":72480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T15:17:01.000Z","msg":"好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c590f4eb76b5f51b724d76d76fbcc93db9c09728","tid":469702,"uid":13586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T15:17:42.000Z","msg":"矛盾大對決"},{"pid":"bd7ff51f8cd8d32957430761cf0dc5747d9afb2c","tid":469702,"uid":72480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T15:18:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想同大家分享</blockquote><br />\n好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0da8d4d90eda0517c6152ade1695901af5f9b690","tid":469702,"uid":72480,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T15:24:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當麻右手連物理攻擊都頂到嘅咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n崎玉唔算係異能人咩,無啦啦一拳可以解決所有野<br />\n<br />\n上條當麻接左會無效化左定還是會反彈比崎玉<br />\n定係會被拳風打到粉身碎骨"},{"pid":"e9a69d2f1482f64b552726cfe3c125d9b871d841","tid":469702,"uid":7477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T15:28:08.000Z","msg":"物理攻擊係當麻既天敵<br />\n但當麻右手斷左會放龍頭<br />\n<br />\n結論 當麻接唔住然後斷手放龍頭咬人"},{"pid":"1208fb53b66a0d4426e79a380b13352e7f5102b5","tid":469702,"uid":13586,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T15:28:16.000Z","msg":"接到，但帶嚟嘅一系列衝擊力唔係一隻右手cover得哂<br />\n<br />\n例如：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/15/232521_31e2135e012f2bfc244f362e65d6dc32.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F15%2F232521_31e2135e012f2bfc244f362e65d6dc32.jpg&h=3d2c09b6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/15/232521_70855fe4a5837e4ba3fb892578897781.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F15%2F232521_70855fe4a5837e4ba3fb892578897781.jpg&h=14257af4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n猶如地震多死人唔係因為地震本身，而係地震帶來嘅二次災害：殺人的唔係地震，係建築物<br />\n<br />\n利申：9up當秘芨"},{"pid":"c190dfdd827a2d46164338f56ea77c955eb51ce7","tid":469702,"uid":13586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T15:31:32.000Z","msg":"漏咗條龍未計添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7d6cf12bae5ab632bb5f60402d4d3a8f67c32c5","tid":469702,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T15:33:50.000Z","msg":"物理層面當麻一定接唔到"},{"pid":"f4a5a175b51d1c56cd691c539e84864fd7c4e090","tid":469702,"uid":2471,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T15:35:46.000Z","msg":"上條當麻學擁有能力幻想殺手<br />\n<br />\n被右手碰觸的<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>超能力</strong></span>或魔法都會被消除，甚至號稱能將<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>神的力量</strong></span>在一瞬間輕鬆抹滅。<br />\n<br />\n你定義左崎玉果一拳係咪超能力同神的力量先"},{"pid":"ffd58d7d874906de9d5b72edc27326b5f992b67b","tid":469702,"uid":48274,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T15:36:30.000Z","msg":"物理攻擊又唔係異能<br />\n應該化解唔到<br />\n食完一拳有咩可能淨係斷左手<br />\n直情死無全屍啦<br />\n仲想出龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f3def7f36a35ca5292fbef482e0b9225ba1fb96","tid":469702,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T15:36:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁一方通行接唔接到？</blockquote><br />\n不如諗下,比一方通行反完<br />\n自己硬食自己一拳頂唔頂得住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一方核彈都接得住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd5e5d8404056ff29618e9bf274cc2dbe27dea68","tid":469702,"uid":91931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T15:38:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁一方通行接唔接到？</blockquote><br />\n不如諗下,比一方通行反完<br />\n自己硬食自己一拳頂唔頂得住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一方核彈都接得住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但係接唔住木原神拳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n岩岩番睇完個本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}